    "title": "Junior Instructional Designer at SRM University Holdings Services",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at SRM University Holdings Services. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Instructional Designer to strengthen our Jodhpur-based team.\n\nAbout SRM University Holdings Services:\nSRM University Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Develop and deliver engaging lesson plans for students\n• Coordinate with academic counselors for student career guidance\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n• Participate in school events, workshops, and training programs\n• Support students with special educational needs\n• Design formative and summative assessments aligned to learning objectives\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Student Assessment\n• Proficiency in Curriculum Development\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in Research Skills\n• Proficiency in LMS Platforms\n• Proficiency in Bloom's Taxonomy\n• Proficiency in Communication Skills\n• Proficiency in Educational Technology\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with SRM University Holdings Services!",
